d lines, \\(I^{\\prime}=r\\)\r\n\\(\\therefore \\frac{1}{I^{\\prime}}=\\frac{\\pi}{3} \\ldots \\quad (2)\\)\r\nFrom and, we get,\r\n\\(\\begin{aligned}\r\n& \\frac{M}{M^{\\prime}}=\\frac{\\pi}{3} \\\\\r\n& \\therefore M^{\\prime}=\\frac{3 M}{\\pi}\r\n\\end{aligned}\\)\r\nHence, \\((C)\\) is the correct answer.\r\nAlternative method:\r\nUsing the short cut formula about bending of a bar magnet, \\(M=\\frac{2 M \\sin \\left(\\frac{\\theta}{2}\\right)}{\\theta}\\)\r\n\\(=\\frac{2 M \\sin 30^{\\circ}}{\\frac{\\pi}{3}}=\\frac{3 M}{\\pi}\\)\r\nHence, (C) is the correct answer.", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGNEPYQ49912287", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "updatedAt": "2024-09-01T07:40:00.066Z", "updated_by": "65d0c176a8f74604505ba6f6", "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["620ab21eb0cb1a4b0ae51f81", "6160241bbb74e5f3d79be031", "6160241c2f0f0966fa72eda6", "61c0899893881c7129ef5166", "61964c8b6b80fda17bcfe142", "6160241a32805db750457ecb", "61e7bd753f352d51145a14ad", "61964c8a0e95e2b64666258e", "61bb8218a216287d869bdc41", "616024195ad23af03d3d3bfd", "629109edc0a0e0ccb07999d8", "629621233563b93ca3bece80", "629f3a91eec7fbad4fc8fac2", "629f390c6ee39ad8a67118ee", "64eb06dd3118f713ecfef1ab", "66d5857ca75f05ee8564f7e5", "67921dab1d5b5072da5e9cf2", "680920383a10446a207fdf7c"], "cpyqbExams": ["616059d70283de43c87e3e24", "616059730283de43c87e3e22"]}}